\par\pard\plain \fi720\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I think I actually inhaled some of those loose crumbs languishing on my desk while I was dozing the booze off. Little crackers invading the wide hairy crevice of my nose. Making their way up into my brain, ready to guide my decisions for the next few days. And they did.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Yuck.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 During the slow hangover of the next day I try to remember the dames face. High cheek bones, thin torso under a ridiculous black trench. Soaking wet blond hair. Was it even raining that night? The words \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93cracker\u8221\'94, \u8220\'93trouble\u8221\'94 and \u8220\'93blond\u8221\'94 swimming through my skull like some gold\u64257\'3Fsh. Cruising through my reality funk.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Oh shit! Eleven am and no donuts yet.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Walking home an hour later I check for the graffiti and notice it gone. Crime scene clear of debris and taped off. I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve made worse decisions than go under that tape and poke around. Lots of garbage, broken handbag with \u8220\'93CAOCH\u8221\'94 printed on the side. Oooh! Is that a lobster? Under the rotting food I \u64257\'3Fnd what might pass for my liver, then under that a box with \u8220\'93trouble\u8221\'94 written in crayon over a saltine logo.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Frank over in narcotics should be able to ID the the prints I managed to get off the old cracker package. Had to slip him the usual fee under his door later that night, he was expecting it. Nice place Frank, I can smell the plastic covering your couch from the hallway.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I get back to the office and start doing some thinking. Well drinking. Some thinking in between the drinking. Mostly drinking with a side of thinking.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Why am I involved in this? There\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s gotta be a hundred other PI\u8217\'92s in the city. Police? I\u8217\'92m sure they\u8217\'92d have noticed the ink on her forehead\u8230\'85probably.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The rotten box though, discarded in a hurry is my guess. Few receipts and an unclaimed prescription for a Methadone clinic. She didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t seem shaky when she visited my office. Other papers pointed to other local joints, gonna do my version of a canvas tomorrow. Wait..what\u8217\'92s gotten into me? Am I hoping for buried treasure? Horny twin sister? One thing I\u8217\'92m sure I\u8217\'92ll \u64257\'3Fnd, written in black ink on the deceased dame, trouble with a capital T.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0}